node.text:
Yummy Sarawak Kolo Mee
Supporting my childhood favorite stall from whom I remembered eating almost everyday! I just would not get sick of it! Contact them in advance to place your order or you can join the queue! But I would highly recommend to call them up first as the queue can be long and slow..
🔻
☎️ 98662244( call 1 hour in advance)
🛵Delivery @deliveroo_sg
🔹
🔹
🔹
🔹

Very bad idea to see this at 122am
Haha!! The aunty is yaya papaya sometimes. But the texture of the noodle is 👍👍👍👍👍.
Did u join the Long and slow queue ahahah
I love Kolo Mee! 😋 There’s a great (and cheaper) one at Tampines round market
Memories of those good old days! 😄👍
I haven't eaten kolo mee in quite a while.  Looks delish. 😍
Wahhh I love Sarawak kolo mee! So shiok especially with chilli!! 😋😋
